runiface_104ghf1665702917603.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ghf1665702917603.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ghf1665702917603.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ghf1665702917603\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Understand the set of service functions provided by Uniface.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ghf1665702917603__p_d130823e1_d130824e1_d130825e1\">Service functions serve the following purposes:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ghf1665702917603__li_d46904e1_d46905e1_d46906e1\">Exchanging information between Uniface and the\n            connector</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ghf1665702917603__li_d46907e1_d46908e1_d46909e1\">Providing functionality required by Uniface, but not\n            supported by the DBMS</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ghf1665702917603__li_d46910e1_d46911e1_d46912e1\">Facilitating the development of a connector</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ghf1665702917603__p_d130826e1_d130827e1_d130828e1\">Many service functions are specific to one corresponding connector request. The description of connector requests includes a list of service functions that can or must be used.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"ghf1665702917603__table_d15668e1_d15669e1_d15670e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"ghf1665702917603__table_d15668e1_d15669e1_d15670e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"ghf1665702917603__table_d15668e1_d15669e1_d15670e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p